This sections lists most of the Skunkware packages in alphabetical order. A more recent listing of the packages available for UnixWare 7 and SCO OpenServer can be found in the Skunkware 7 Component List and the Skunkware 98 Component List.

The "package name" can be used to install that particular component as follows:
On UnixWare, issue the command 

    # pkgadd -d /dev/cdrom/cdrom1 package_name

On OpenServer, issue the command 

    # # custom -p SKUNK98:default:package_name -i -m /dev/rcd0
